TODO. surefire插件在test phase阶段执行单元测试，生成测试报告文件
1. 当同时存在JUnit4和JUnit5的单元测试时，Plugin可能选择不同的Provider，导致J4测试不执行 !!
2. <version>3.0.0</version>版本会抛出异常 Failure to find org.apache.maven.surefire:surefire-junit-platform:jar:3.0.0
<plugin>
    <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
    <artifactId>maven-surefire-plugin</artifactId>
    <version>3.0.0-M3</version>
    [... configuration or goals and executions ...]
</plugin>

生成web版的测试报告 under ${basedir}/target/surefire-reports
<plugin>
    <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
    <artifactId>maven-surefire-report-plugin</artifactId>
    <version>3.0.0-M3</version>
</plugin>
